952 /* 0x190 (AON_WDT_CRT)
953  01:00 rw 00/01/11: turn on AON Watchdog 10: turn off AON Watchdog 2'b10
954  02 rw 1: WDG countine count in DLPS 0:WDG stop count in DLPS 1'b0
955  03 rw 1: reset whole chip 0: reset whole chip - (AON register and RTC) 1'b0
956  04 rw when reg_aon_wdt_cnt_ctl == 0 1'b0
957  1:relaod counter when exit DLPS 0:not reload counter when exit DLPS
958  07:04 rw
959  25:08 rw Set the period of AON watchdog (unit:1/450Hz ~ 1/2.3KHz) 8'hff
960  31:26 rw
961 */

963 {
964  uint32_t d32;

966  {

969  uint32_t reg_aon_wdt_rst_lv_sel: 1; // 03
970  uint32_t reg_aon_wdt_cnt_reload: 1; // 04
971  uint32_t rsvd0: 3; // 07:05
972  uint32_t reg_aon_wdt_comp: 18; // 25:08
973  uint32_t rsvd1: 6; // 31:26
974  };
975 } RTC_AON_WDT_CRT_TYPE;

981 */

4377 #define SWAP32(x) ((uint32_t)( \
4378  (((uint32_t)(x) & (uint32_t)0x000000ff) << 24) | \
4379  (((uint32_t)(x) & (uint32_t)0x0000ff00) << 8) | \
4380  (((uint32_t)(x) & (uint32_t)0x00ff0000) >> 8) | \
4381  (((uint32_t)(x) & (uint32_t)0xff000000) >> 24)))
4382 
4383 #define WAP16(x) ((uint16_t)( \
4384  (((uint16_t)(x) & (uint16_t)0x00ff) << 8) | \
4385  (((uint16_t)(x) & (uint16_t)0xff00) >> 8)))
4386 
4387 #if SYSTEM_ENDIAN == LITTLE_ENDIAN
4388 #ifndef rtk_le16_to_cpu
4389 #define rtk_cpu_to_le32(x) ((uint32_t)(x))
4390 #define rtk_le32_to_cpu(x) ((uint32_t)(x))
4391 #define rtk_cpu_to_le16(x) ((uint16_t)(x))
4392 #define rtk_le16_to_cpu(x) ((uint16_t)(x))
4393 #define rtk_cpu_to_be32(x) SWAP32((x))
4394 #define rtk_be32_to_cpu(x) SWAP32((x))
4395 #define rtk_cpu_to_be16(x) WAP16((x))
4396 #define rtk_be16_to_cpu(x) WAP16((x))
4397 #endif
4398 
4399 #elif SYSTEM_ENDIAN == BIG_ENDIAN
4400 #ifndef rtk_le16_to_cpu
4401 #define rtk_cpu_to_le32(x) SWAP32((x))
4402 #define rtk_le32_to_cpu(x) SWAP32((x))
4403 #define rtk_cpu_to_le16(x) WAP16((x))
4404 #define rtk_le16_to_cpu(x) WAP16((x))
4405 #define rtk_cpu_to_be32(x) ((uint32_t)(x))
4406 #define rtk_be32_to_cpu(x) ((uint32_t)(x))
4407 #define rtk_cpu_to_be16(x) ((uint16_t)(x))
4408 #define rtk_be16_to_cpu(x) ((uint16_t)(x))
4409 #endif
4410 #endif

4412 #define HAL_READ32(base, addr) \
4413  rtk_le32_to_cpu(*((volatile uint32_t *)(base + addr)))
4414 
4415 #define HAL_WRITE32(base, addr, value32) \
4416  ((*((volatile uint32_t *)(base + addr))) = rtk_cpu_to_le32(value32))
4417 
4418 #define HAL_UPDATE32(addr, mask, value32) \
4419  HAL_WRITE32(0, addr, (HAL_READ32(0, addr) & ~(mask)) | ((value32) & (mask)))
4420 
4421 #define HAL_READ16(base, addr) \
4422  rtk_le16_to_cpu(*((volatile uint16_t *)(base + addr)))
4423 
4424 #define HAL_WRITE16(base, addr, value) \
4425  ((*((volatile uint16_t *)(base + addr))) = rtk_cpu_to_le16(value))
4426 
4427 #define HAL_UPDATE16(addr, mask, value16) \
4428  HAL_WRITE16(0, addr, (HAL_READ16(0, addr) & ~(mask)) | ((value16) & (mask)))
4429

4431  (*((volatile uint8_t *)(base + addr)))
4432

4435
